code: @Override public ConditionOutcome getMatchOutcome(ConditionContext context, AnnotatedTypeMetadata metadata) {     BindResult<?> property = Binder.get(context.getEnvironment()).bind(this.propertyName, STRING_LIST).     ConditionMessage.Builder messageBuilder = this.messageBuilder.get().     if (property.isBound()) {         return ConditionOutcome.match(messageBuilder.found("property").items(this.propertyName)).     }     return ConditionOutcome.noMatch(messageBuilder.didNotFind("property").items(this.propertyName)). }
